{"data":[{"date":"17:37 18/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Chievo vs Juventus 23h00 ng\u00e0y 18/8 (Serie A 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/18/chievo-vs-juventus-serie-a-1882018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Chievo vs Juventus: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chievo vs Juventus v\u00f2ng 1 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Italia Serie A 2018/19 l\u00fac 23h00 \u0111\u00eam ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 18/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ea3m h\u1ecda s\u1eadp c\u1ea7u Morandi \u1edf Genoa khi\u1ebfn 39 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thi\u1ec7t m\u1ea1ng \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng trong nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y qua. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c, v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n Serie A 2018-19 v\u1eabn s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0 t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Juventus t\u1ea1i Marc'Antonio Bentegodi, s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac 9 n\u0103m ho\u00e0ng kim c\u00f9ng Real Madrid v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u1edbi Juventus. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ec9 l\u1ee5c v\u1edbi 1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 33. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi Juventus, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 canh b\u1ea1c m\u00e0 coi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Chievo vs Juventus b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd Serie A h\u00f4m nay 188 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Chievo vs Juventus b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd Serie A h\u00f4m nay 188 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/nhan-dinh-chievo-vs-juventus-23h00-ngay-188-serie-a-201819.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chievo vs Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nJuventus c\u00f3 l\u00fd do ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u00cdt nh\u1ea5t, Nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1edf n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e3n nguy\u1ec7n khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u01a1n s\u1ed1t m\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra \u1edf m\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc \u1ee7ng. S\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ec9 l\u1ee5c b\u00e1n ra l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng cho s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. N\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n mang l\u1ea1i cho Juventus nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u1ebfch x\u00f9 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf khi L\u00e3o b\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1t Champions League \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec9nh \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng hay kh\u00f4ng, v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee3i t\u1edbi cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, ho\u1eb7c th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 2-3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u1eefa. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00eam nay, Cristiano Ronaldo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ngay \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft Serie A. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn SV\u0110 Marc'Antonio Bentegodi s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u1ed7 tr\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCris Ronaldo s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c! Anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a NHM v\u00e0 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Serie A d\u00e0nh cho s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. \u0110\u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 CR7 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede Real Madrid, Cris Ronaldo th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o l\u1ec7ch tr\u00e1i. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft Juventus \u0111\u00eam nay, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Allegri \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 CR7 gia t\u0103ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u, h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Serie A, chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 9 n\u0103m, Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 khai h\u1ecfa, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Deportivo v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-2. \u0110\u00eam nay, CR7 k\u00ec v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n th\u1ebf khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Juventus ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 Chievo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5633","checkdouble":"194755"},{"date":"15:30 18/08","title":"B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i ch\u1ec9 ra g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/bao-thai-chi-ra-guong-mat-duoc-ky-vong-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1edd b\u00e1o th\u1ec3 thao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Th\u00e1i Lan, SiamSport m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u1ea3n danh s\u00e1ch 9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng xem nh\u1ea5t ASIAD 2018, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2>B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i ch\u1ec9 ra g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\u00a0 <o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1edd SiamSport \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ec3 t\u00ean 9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng xem nh\u1ea5t ASIAD 2018. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. Trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u00f9 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, anh \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. D\u00f9 \u1edf\u00a0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0ng nh\u1edd t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i ch\u1ec9 ra g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i ch\u1ec9 ra g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/cong-phuong_vwzy.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ecdt\u00a0danh s\u00e1ch 9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng xem nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, t\u1edd SiamSport b\u1ea7u ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng xem nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i sau lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Pakistan v\u1eeba qua, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ch\u00fa \u00fd khi s\u00fat h\u1ecfng \u0111\u1ebfn 2 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n tuy nhi\u00ean, anh v\u1eabn c\u00f3 cho ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi tung ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n cho Quang H\u1ea3i m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. Sau hai l\u1ea7n s\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1ee3t penalty, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eeb pha che ch\u1eafn th\u00f4ng minh v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1eddi Olympic Pakistan. V\u00ec l\u00fd do \u0111\u00f3, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, SiamSport c\u00f2n nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi Son Heung-min, Lee Seung-woo (H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c), Beto Goncalves (Indonesia), Mohammed Darwish (Palestine), Adel Bader (Qatar), Zhang Yuning (Trung Qu\u1ed1c), Aung Thu (Myanmar) v\u00e0 Supachai (Th\u00e1i Lan). \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u1edf ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5632","checkdouble":"194745"},{"date":"15:42 18/08","title":"HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung: \u201c\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u00e1i Lan\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/hlv-mai-duc-chung-dt-viet-nam-se-danh-bai-thai-lan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 18 di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 18h30 ng\u00e0y 19/8 t\u1edbi, HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u00e1i Lan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u00e1i Lan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/HLV-Mai-Duc-Chung-DT-Viet-Nam-se-danh-bai-Thai-Lan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i \u1edf ASIAD</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e1 th\u0103m may r\u1ee7i \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef ASIAD 2018. Theo \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm 2 t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u00f4 g\u00e1i v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1edfi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp n\u1ebfu h\u1ea1 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 19 t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2: \u201cX\u00e9t v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m v\u00f3c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n tuy\u1ec3n n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan lu\u00f4n k\u1ecb gi\u01a1 nhau v\u1edbi nhau. K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng SEA Games v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, Th\u00e1i Lan kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fang ta. \u1ede AFF Cup 2018, Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i Th\u00e1i Lan. Qua theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung cao nh\u1ea5t. N\u1ebfu gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 99%. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y\u201d.\u00a0<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-mai-duc-chung-chi-ra-2-dieu-kien-de-dt-viet-nam-du-world-cup-465-188358.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/hlv-mai-duc-chung-chi-ra-2-dieu-kien-de-dt-viet-nam-du-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-mai-duc-chung-chi-ra-2-dieu-kien-de-dt-viet-nam-du-world-cup-465-188358.html\">HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung ch\u1ec9 ra 2 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 World Cup</span><br>\r\nHLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n d\u1ef1 World Cup, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u00ean ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n hai v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/nu-viet-nam-vs-nu-myanmar-16h00-ngay-hom-nay-137-372-191100.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/video-tong-hop-nu-viet-nam-30-nu-myanmar-aff-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/nu-viet-nam-vs-nu-myanmar-16h00-ngay-hom-nay-137-372-191100.html\">N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 N\u1eef Myanmar (KT): Th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm, n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111o\u1ea1t h\u1ea1ng 3 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1</span><br>\r\nG\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng th\u1eafng 4-3 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh h\u1ea1ng 3 chung cu\u1ed9c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef \u0110\u00f4ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/nu-viet-nam-vs-nu-australia-16h00-ngay-117-372-190944.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/nu-viet-nam-vs-nu-australia-16h00-ngay-117.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/nu-viet-nam-vs-nu-australia-16h00-ngay-117-372-190944.html\">N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-4 U20 N\u1eef Australia (KT): Thua b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e0nh tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 khu v\u1ef1c</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0111\u00e3 thua to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Australia \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018. Tuy\u1ebft Dung l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi c\u1ea3 hai b\u00e0n cho...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5631","checkdouble":"194746"},{"date":"16:21 18/08","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/nguoi-nhat-se-dung-thu-mon-du-bi-de-dau-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh Kojima Ryosuke d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan n\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Pakistan c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt h\u00f4m, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt l\u00e0 Kojima Ryosuke \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 90 ph\u00fat sau va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i l\u1edbn cho Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u00f9 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t n\u1eb7ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/a6-3120-1534566074.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Obi Obinna l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Pakistan, ch\u00ednh HLV Moriyasu Hajime c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u00f4ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i VCK U20 World Cup c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 1 n\u0103m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cKojima Ryosuke d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n s\u1edbm \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\u201d, HLV Moriyasu Hajime cho bi\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y, Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Obi Obinna cho tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Obi Obinna l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 b\u1ed1 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nigeria. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc, anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u1edf ph\u00fat 77 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft thay cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Ryosuke. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u00e2m l\u00fd khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 b\u1eaft ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i\u201d, Obi n\u00f3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 t\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed9i th\u1eafng \u1edf c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D v\u00e0 s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 \u1edf 1 trong 3 b\u1ea3ng B/E/F \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out.\u00a0<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-olympic-viet-nam-chat-luong-hon-sau-giai-u23-chau-a-2018-472-194738.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-olympic-viet-nam-chat-luong-hon-sau-giai-u23-chau-a-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-olympic-viet-nam-chat-luong-hon-sau-giai-u23-chau-a-2018-472-194738.html\">HLV Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n sau gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018</span><br />\r\n\u00d4ng Hajime Moriyasu \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang-seo \u1edf ASIAD 18 v\u00ec l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5630","checkdouble":"194747"},{"date":"17:28 18/08","title":"H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c thua Malaysia: Coi ch\u1eebng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/han-quoc-thua-malaysia-coi-chung-bi-loai-nhu-nguoi-duc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i v\u00e0o v\u1ebft xe \u0111\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i World Cup.</h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>S\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 quan khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u00f4i sao Son Heung-min \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan, d\u00f9 h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd nh\u1ea5t cho t\u1ea5m HCV \u1edf k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cOlympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111i m\u1ed9t h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i xem m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung. Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eebng b\u1ecb H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c h\u1ea1 \u1edf World Cup, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thua b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o \u1edf ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y\u201d.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c thua Malaysia Coi ch\u1eebng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c thua Malaysia Coi ch\u1eebng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/Han-Quoc-thua-Malaysia-Coi-chung-bi-loai-nhu-nguoi-Duc-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Son Heung-min t\u1eebng c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o \u1edf ASIAD</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb BHL \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 ngo\u00e0i tai. B\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau khi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c thua Malaysia, HLV Kim Hak-bum\u00a0\u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 quan khi xem th\u01b0\u1eddng n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Malaysia.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"T\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tin n\u1ed5i \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t sai l\u1ea7m. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 ch\u1ee7 quan khi xoay tua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi 3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3 t\u1ea1o ra qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u00e1 nhanh, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra th\u00eam b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o n\u1eefa\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 xem th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Malaysia khi kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc t\u1ea1i World Cup v\u1eeba qua l\u00e0 Jo Hyeon-Woo v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Son Heung-min ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ngay c\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 \"Messi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c\" Lee Seung-Woo c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Malaysia\" title=\"Olympic Malaysia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/u23-malaysia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Tuy nhi\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n v\u1eabn ch\u1ee7 quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Malaysia</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 quan \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n c\u0103n b\u1ea3n khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn tr\u1eadn thua t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i. H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 s\u1eafc s\u1ea3o c\u00f2n h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eebng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ASIAD 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi sau m\u00e0n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Safawi Rasid. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng mu\u1ed9n m\u00e0n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Kim chi trong hi\u1ec7p 2 ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u00ea ch\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi m\u1ea5t lu\u00f4n ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0o tay \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y, c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c hai \u0111\u1ed9i Kyrgyzstan v\u00e0 Bahrain c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a nhau 2-2 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Kim Hak-bum c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thua \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh n\u00e0o s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1eebng khi\u1ebfn \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3i \u00ea ch\u1ec1 r\u1eddi World Cup 2018 ngay sau v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng, d\u00f9 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Joachim Loew khi \u0111\u00f3 \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 nh\u1ee5c nh\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Kyrgyzstan song \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c th\u1eafng \u0110\u1ee9c hay H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c thua Malaysia l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng y\u1ebfu ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 20/8, Kyrgyzstan \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi ASIAD ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Han Quoc\" title=\"Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/000041717300120180818000827458-153452891502058465001-0935.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3\u00a0b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018 n\u1ebfu thua Kyrgyzstan</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y\u00a0Son Heung-min v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i\u00a0\u0111ang t\u1ea1m x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, h\u01a1n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Kyrgyzstan v\u00e0 Bahrain 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Tuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y ho\u1eb7c t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n n\u1eefa l\u00e0 s\u1ebd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu Kyrgyzstan th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n tr\u00ean BXH. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu Bahrain th\u1eafng Malaysia, khi \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y \u00c1 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c bi\u1ebfn Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Malaysia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i \u1edf th\u1ebf ch\u00e2n t\u01b0\u1eddng, Bahrain r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Do \u0111\u00f3, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ea3 Bahrain v\u00e0 Kyrgyzstan c\u00f9ng th\u1eafng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i, Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u201cx\u00e1ch vali\u201d v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i k\u1ebft bu\u1ed3n cho Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Son Heung-min khi anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf c\u1ea3 gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u1ec3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u00ecm t\u1ea5m HC v\u00e0ng \u1edf k\u1ef3 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. D\u1eabu sao, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn c\u00f2n 90 ph\u00fat \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Kyrgyzstan s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa sai l\u1ea7m n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"ASIAD bang E\" title=\"ASIAD b\u1ea3ng E\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/1.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea3ng E sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/son-heungmin-xau-ho-sau-tran-thua-soc-truoc-malaysia-168-194744.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/Han-Quoc-thua-Malaysia-Coi-chung-bi-loai-nhu-nguoi-Duc-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/son-heungmin-xau-ho-sau-tran-thua-soc-truoc-malaysia-168-194744.html\">Son Heung-min x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Tottenham, Son Heung-Min \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau khi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i qua 17/8.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-ong-kim-swee-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-ky-tich-truoc-han-quoc-168-194743.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/hlv-ong-kim-swee-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-ky-tich-truoc-han-quoc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-ong-kim-swee-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-ky-tich-truoc-han-quoc-168-194743.html\">HLV Ong Kim Swee n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng k\u1ef3 t\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn Malaysia 2-1 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, HLV Ong Kim Swee v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng t\u1ecf ra h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng d\u00f9 v\u1eeba t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed cho n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-malaysia-phan-khich-voi-chien-tich-danh-bai-han-quoc-168-194742.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/truyen-thong-malaysia-phan-khich-voi-chien-tich-danh-bai-han-quoc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-malaysia-phan-khich-voi-chien-tich-danh-bai-han-quoc-168-194742.html\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Malaysia ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span><br>\r\nGi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Malaysia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ecbp \u201cn\u1ed5 tung tr\u1eddi\u201d sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-u23-malaysia-21-u23-han-quoc-asiad-2018-331-194701.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/video-tong-hop-u23-malaysia-21-u23-han-quoc-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-u23-malaysia-21-u23-han-quoc-asiad-2018-331-194701.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: U23 Malaysia 2-1 U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (ASIAD 2018)</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a khu v\u1ef1c \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u Asiad 2018 \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd khi xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 c\u00f3 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ng\u00f4i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5629","checkdouble":"194754"},{"date":"17:55 18/08","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo chia s\u1ebb \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/14/hlv-park-hang-seo-chia-se-dieu-gi-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2>HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n? <o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y mai 19/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam e ng\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t d\u00f9 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u \u1edf l\u1ee9a tu\u1ed5i U21.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/HLV-Park-Hang-Seo-noi-gi-truoc-tran-gap-Olympic-Nhat-Ban-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam Park Hang Seo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Park Hang Seo cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cCh\u00fang ta bi\u1ebft Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. N\u0103m nay h\u1ecd c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U21 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho Olympic 2020. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 U21 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh. 15 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p. 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t th\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ecd c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n n\u00ean r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t chu \u0111\u00e1o cho Asiad 2018. Theo t\u00f4i, 21 tu\u1ed5i hay 23 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn \u0111\u00e2u. H\u1ecd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y mai\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean BXH b\u1ea3ng D l\u00fac n\u00e0y, hai \u0111\u1ed9i Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111ang b\u1eb1ng nhau \u1edf m\u1ecdi ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1, n\u1ebfu \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi hai \u0111\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i trong 90 ph\u00fat, th\u00ec h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 \u1edf m\u1ed9t trong 3 b\u1ea3ng B/E/F song c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh n\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng D c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-ket-qua-tai-asiad-2018-472-193923.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, NHM \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t lo th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo ph\u1ea3i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 hai b\u1ea3ng D v\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng E l\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, song m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Kim chi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n ph\u1ea3i \u201ctr\u00e1nh n\u00e9\u201d Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00d4ng t\u00e2m s\u1ef1: \u201cT\u00f4i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng n\u00f3i v\u1edbi ai l\u00e0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam mu\u00f4n tr\u00e1nh Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u1ea3. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang ta bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 Malaysia h\u00f4m qua \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-nhat-se-dung-thu-mon-du-bi-de-dau-olympic-viet-nam-168-194747.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/han-quoc-thua-malaysia-coi-chung-bi-loai-nhu-nguoi-duc-168-194754.html\">H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c thua Malaysia: Coi ch\u1eebng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-thai-chi-ra-guong-mat-duoc-ky-vong-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad-168-194745.html\">B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i ch\u1ec9 ra g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ASIAD</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/son-heungmin-xau-ho-sau-tran-thua-soc-truoc-malaysia-168-194744.html\">Son Heung-min 'x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5' sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-ong-kim-swee-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-ky-tich-truoc-han-quoc-168-194743.html\">HLV Ong Kim Swee n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng k\u1ef3 t\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5628","checkdouble":"194756"},{"date":"13:51 18/08","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Chelsea: Jorginho l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/huyen-thoai-chelsea-jorginho-la-nguoi-truyen-dao-cua-hlv-sarri.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Chelsea Dennis Wise \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italy v\u00e0 coi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch quan tr\u1ecdng trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a CLB.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\"T\u00f4i th\u1ea5y th\u00edch t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Maurizio Sarri mang v\u1ec1. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Jorginho l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc\", Dennis Wise m\u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u bu\u1ed5i ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n v\u1edbi t\u1edd Goal. \"T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 theo d\u00f5i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 th\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1edfi c\u00e1ch Jorginho l\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng, g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ed1i nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u theo \u00fd mu\u1ed1n. Mang v\u1ec1 Jorginho, Chelsea s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi hi\u1ec3u tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Sarri v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebft ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nJorginho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italy ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. Trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a 2018-2019, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Napoli gi\u1eef vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ea7u n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00f3ng v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tung ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nhanh t\u1eeb s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/huyen-thoai-khen-ngoi-tan-binh-bom-tan-cua-chelsea-het-loi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0Jorginho l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong h\u00e8 2018. \u1ea2nh: PA</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nWise \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00e0n em. C\u1ef1u \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: \"Khi m\u1ed9t HLV c\u00f3 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch ch\u1ec9 huy \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1t ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a HLV, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng c\u00f3 \u00edch cho \u00f4ng \u1ea5y. Jorginho ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng, \u0111\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 s\u1ebd theo c\u1eadu \u1ea5y h\u1ebft m\u00f9a n\u00e0y\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDanh th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho Sarri tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn derby th\u00e0nh London t\u1ed1i th\u1ee9 b\u1ea3y 18/8. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: \"\u00d4ng \u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c 21 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Si\u00eau Cup Anh g\u1eb7p Man City. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian qu\u00e1 ng\u1eafn \u0111\u1ec3 Sarri thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1eeb h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng 3-4-3 sang 4-3-3\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 Chelsea c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi v\u00e0 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi su\u00f4n s\u1ebb, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m trong s\u1ed1 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay Man City v\u00e0 Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRoman Abramovich b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri kh\u00f4ng ngo\u00e0i m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch gi\u00fap Chelsea t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n. Dennis Wise tin nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italy s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ec7c. \u00d4ng chia s\u1ebb: \"\u0110i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Chelsea, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch pressing c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 cao. H\u1ecd lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t so v\u1edbi Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 Antonio Conte, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00edch \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, Sarri s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n c\u00f9 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, h\u00f2ng b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1n s\u1ee9c n\u00e0y\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 y\u00eau m\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169, Wise cho r\u1eb1ng Chelsea kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi Man City. \u00d4ng ph\u00e2n t\u00edch: \"Ai c\u0169ng nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o Chelsea, v\u00e0o k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 100 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i. T\u00f4i th\u00ec ch\u1ec9 hy v\u1ecdng, Chelsea s\u1ebd r\u00fat ng\u1eafn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi h\u1ecd n\u0103m nay\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1966 c\u0169ng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o xanh v\u1ec1 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ef1 m\u00e3n, n\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng cao: \"Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c hay trong n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Conte v\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. Nh\u01b0ng n\u0103m nay t\u00f4i tin, kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t C\u0110V Chelsea n\u00e0o k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c l\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ngay m\u00f9a \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Sarri\". <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>Dennis Wise, 51 tu\u1ed5i, t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i 11 n\u0103m cho Chelsea t\u1eeb 1990 \u0111\u1ebfn 2001. \u00d4ng  gi\u1eef b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1993, v\u00e0 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o  Chelsea nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 b\u1ea3y trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<br>\r\n</em><br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng H\u1ee3p (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5627","checkdouble":"194737"},{"date":"14:19 18/08","title":"Liverpool CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C thanh l\u00fd \"h\u00e0ng t\u1ed3n\" Klavan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/liverpool-chinh-thuc-thanh-ly-hang-ton-klavan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf v\u00f9ng Merseyside \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Estonia, Ragnar Klavan cho CLB Cagliari t\u1ea1i Serie A.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Cagliari c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7 v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam qua, ch\u1ec9 \u00edt gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u1edf Serie A \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda. M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Cagliari ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nh\u01b0ng theo SkySport h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 cho Liverpool s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00e0 2 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool b\u00e1n Klavan sang Cagliari h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool b\u00e1n Klavan sang Cagliari h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/180818_093855_175.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Liverpool b\u00e1n Klavan sang Cagliari</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRagnar Klavan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00ed b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 2 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Cagliari, k\u00e8m theo \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gia h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m. Anh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00ed h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Cagliari ch\u1ec9 10 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 \u1edf Serie A k\u1ebft th\u00fac.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRagnar Klavan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u1eeb Augsburg v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2016. Trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Estonia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 53 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, anh ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a HLV Klopp \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, sau khi Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Van Dijk, Klavan ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng \u00edt c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi trong phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Klavan c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Liverpool g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 b\u1edfi trong tay HLV Klopp hi\u1ec7n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 trung v\u1ec7 th\u1ef1c th\u1ee5 l\u00e0 Van Dijk, Lovren v\u00e0 Joel Matip. Do \u0111\u00f3, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Gomez nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKlopp \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Gomez nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y do anh ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Clyne v\u00e0 Alexander-Arnold \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5626","checkdouble":"194741"},{"date":"16:23 18/08","title":"5 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi ch\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi trong tr\u1eadn derby London k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/5-cau-hoi-cho-duoc-tra-loi-trong-tran-derby-london.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea vs Arsenal trong k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi, c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eefng di\u1ec7n m\u1ea1o m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri v\u00e0 Unai Emery. Ai s\u1ebd m\u1ec9m c\u01b0\u1eddi sau cu\u1ed1i trong tr\u1eadn derby London \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh?</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>1. Arsenal ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng kh\u1eafc ch\u1ebf Chelsea t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng?</b></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">Arsenal ch\u01a1i ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u00f2n Chelsea ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u2013 nghe m\u1edbi th\u1eadt l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm l\u00e0m sao nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y d\u01b0\u1edbi hai tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Unai Emery v\u00e0 Maurizio Sarri.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">Arsenal c\u1ee7a Emery s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng phong c\u00e1ch pressing quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 ch\u1ecdn l\u1ecdc, b\u00f3p ngh\u1eb9t kh\u00f4ng gian gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c l\u1edbp ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1c. Duy tr\u00ec c\u1ef1 ly nh\u1ecf h\u1eb9p v\u00e0 g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t quan tr\u1ecdng cho c\u1ea3 khi ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 l\u1eabn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Arsenal derby London h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"5 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Arsenal derby London h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/5-cau-hoi-nhan-dinh-Chelsea-vs-Arsenal-derby-London-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Arsenal derby London v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n, Chelsea c\u1ee7a Sarri s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chi\u1ebfm l\u0129nh th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng 4-3-3 r\u1ed9ng kh\u1eafp v\u00e0 c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng, bi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn derby London kh\u00f4ng Arsene Wenger \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 22 n\u0103m tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n gi\u1eefa hai tr\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00e1i ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">Arsenal tr\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebb \u0111ang c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n. K\u1ebf s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Manchester City nh\u01b0ng suy cho c\u00f9ng, \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">Emery mu\u1ed1n d\u1eabn d\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e2ng cao, \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a \u00e1p l\u1ef1c trong t\u1ea7m ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 l\u00ean tr\u00ean v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng kh\u00f4ng gian c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khai th\u00e1c. M\u1ed9t Chelsea v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n giao gi\u1eefa hai tri\u1ebft l\u00fd \u0111\u1ed1i l\u1eadp gi\u1eefa Antonio Conte v\u00e0 Sarri r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd s\u1eadp b\u1eaby.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black\">2. Ozil c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh \u00fap Jorginho?<o:p></o:p></span></b></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">Ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Man City, Arsenal ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1 b\u00f3 h\u1eb9p, v\u1edbi Aaron Ramsey t\u1eeb gi\u1eefa d\u00e2ng cao h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 trung phong </span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:black\">Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang, trong khi Mesut Ozil v\u00e0 Henrikh Mkhitaryan l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng hai c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i tr\u00e1i.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi ch\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi trong tr\u1eadn derby London k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"5 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi ch\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi trong tr\u1eadn derby London k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/5-cau-hoi-cho-duoc-tra-loi-trong-tran-derby-London-ky-nguyen-moi-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Arsenal derby London v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fac \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xoay chuy\u1ec3n th\u00e0nh 4-3-1-2 v\u1edbi Ozil \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed l\u00f9i s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m c\u1ea7u n\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ee3t ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n Arsenal. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City, nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n ngay ngo\u00e0i r\u00eca v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u00edt ch\u1ea1m trong th\u1ebf b\u1ecb \u00e1p s\u00e1t v\u00e0 tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean tr\u00ean cho Aubameyang v\u00e0 Ramsey.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black\">Chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt n\u00e0y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t huy tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh t\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd Jorginho v\u1eabn \u0111ang v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng gi\u00e0u t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 10 thu\u1ea7n t\u00fay v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t t\u1eadn s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed b\u1ecb ch\u00ednh Emery \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi \u00fd th\u1ee9c ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng Ozil v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c x\u1edbi tung tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u1ed1n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh tr\u01a1n tru v\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m.<span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black\">3. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi ai \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u00e0 Guendouzi?<o:p></o:p></span></b></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">T\u1eeb Napoli \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea, b\u1ed9 ba ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Sarri s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n bao g\u1ed3m m\u1ed9t ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, m\u1ed9t box-to-box v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, v\u1edbi m\u1eaft x\u00edch cao nh\u1ea5t cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng kia th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u00ean tr\u00e1i v\u00e0 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u0103n \u00fd v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh \u0111\u00f3 (Lorenzo Insigne \u1edf Napoli v\u00e0 Eden Hazard \u1edf Chelsea).<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i cho Chelsea \u1edf tr\u1eadn derby London b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ee9ng b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Matteo Guendouzi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng, \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch \u1edf m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb non n\u1edbt, thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m chinh chi\u1ebfn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao ch\u1ee9 \u0111\u1eebng n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n m\u1edbi ch\u00e2n \u01b0\u1edbt ch\u00e2n r\u00e1o \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Premier League.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi ch\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi trong tr\u1eadn derby London k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"5 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi ch\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi trong tr\u1eadn derby London k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/5-cau-hoi-cho-duoc-tra-loi-trong-tran-derby-London-ky-nguyen-moi-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Arsenal derby London v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">C\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, Guendouzi ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh anh \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i l\u1edbn trong b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u00e1p s\u00e1t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Raheem Sterling, \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i d\u1eaft b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 v\u00e0 tung c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00e1y l\u01b0\u1edbi Petr Cech.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 ai s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 ba tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Sarri, s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh qu\u1ea3 bom t\u1ea5n Jorginho v\u00e0 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi N\u2019Golo Kante? T\u00e2n HLV Chelsea r\u1ea5t th\u00edch Ross Barkley nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a h\u01a1n nh\u01b0 Ruben Loftus-Cheek v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t Mateo Kovacic, t\u00e2n binh Croatia m\u1edbi m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Real Madrid, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao Everton \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u \u00e1i c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n sau nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black\">4. Hazard v\u00e0 Pedro c\u00e0y n\u00e1t hai c\u00e1nh Arsenal?<o:p></o:p></span></b></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1n kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n th\u1eddi \u1edf Emirates khi c\u1ea3 ba s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng (Sead Kolasinac, Nacho Monreal, </span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black\">Ainsley Maitland-Niles)<span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\nbold\">, \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed g\u00e2y \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1ea5t cho t\u00e2n HLV Emery b\u1edfi \u0111\u1eb7c th\u00f9 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng.<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">L\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ee7 ngu\u1ed3n l\u1ef1c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 cho c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean m\u00e0 v\u1eabn duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ef1 ly \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh b\u00f3 h\u1eb9p v\u00e0 nh\u1ecf g\u1ecdn? Man City \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4 l\u1eadp </span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\ncolor:black\">Maitland-Niles v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Stephan Lichtsteiner tr\u00e1i k\u00e8o sau \u0111\u00f3 qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch nh\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng cho Riyad Mahrez, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 Sarri l\u01b0u t\u00e2m cho h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 Pedro Rodriguez.<span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi ch\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi trong tr\u1eadn derby London k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"5 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi ch\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi trong tr\u1eadn derby London k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/5-cau-hoi-cho-duoc-tra-loi-trong-tran-derby-London-ky-nguyen-moi-hinh-anh-4.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Arsenal derby London v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black\">H\u00e0nh lang \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n b\u00ean kia th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1ng lo ng\u1ea1i h\u01a1n cho Arsenal, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 khu v\u1ef1c kh\u1edfi ngu\u1ed3n hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a Man City v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1edd n\u00f3 c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfm l\u0129nh b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Eden Hazard. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black\">Hector Bellerin v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 th\u00edch d\u00e2ng cao, trong khi Lacazette d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn thuy\u00ean gi\u1ea3m kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1eeb tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean. Ozil c\u00f3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ea5y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao \u1edf kho\u1ea3n n\u00e0y, v\u1eady n\u00ean hy v\u1ecdng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o Lucas Torreira, t\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay t\u1eebng b\u1eaft ch\u1ebft c\u1ea3 Cristiano Ronaldo \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 h\u1ed3i World Cup 2018 h\u01a1n th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black\">5. Aubameyang v\u00e0 Lacazette h\u00e0nh h\u1ea1 c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 Chelsea?<o:p></o:p></span></b></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Sarri tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng David Luiz ch\u1ec9 c\u00e0ng ch\u1ee9ng minh ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m Conte \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00fang khi b\u1ecf r\u01a1i anh tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, b\u1ea5t lu\u1eadn ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hay kh\u00f4ng. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh t\u1eeb l\u00e2u, \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City \u1edf Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh hay k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng \u1edf Huddersfield Town, n\u01a1i anh d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ecb Steve Mounie v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i trong nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Aubameyang Lacazette\" title=\"Aubameyang Lacazette\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/hoc-tro-mach-emery-cach-dua-arsenal-tim-lai-chien-thang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Arsenal derby London v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c Antonio Rudiger c\u0169ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t y\u1ebfu trong kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadp trung. N\u00f3i c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 l\u00e0 t\u1eed huy\u1ec7t c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng oan, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1edfi Chelsea v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sarri cho l\u00e0m quen vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea3m t\u1eeb ba ng\u01b0\u1eddi xu\u1ed1ng hai trong b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 v\u1ec7.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, sau h\u01a1n n\u1eeda ti\u1ebfng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c d\u00f9 thua Man City, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t gi\u00fap Arsenal d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 d\u1ed3n \u00e9p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 co c\u1ee5m h\u01a1n, Lacazette ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh v\u1edbi Aubameyang t\u1ea1o n\u00ean c\u1eb7p song s\u00e1t xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u1edf Stamford Bridge.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">Cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m ra sao c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 khi k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Gabon n\u00e0y, v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 kinh ho\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 reo r\u1eafc kh\u1ed1n kh\u1ed5 cho m\u1ecdi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, hu\u1ed1ng h\u1ed3 chi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u00ec v\u00e0 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p nh\u01b0 Luiz v\u00e0 Rudiger. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Arsenal derby London:<br>\r\n</span></strong></h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-chelsea-vs-arsenal-23h30-ngay-188-dung-lay-man-city-lam-thuoc-do-172-194717.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/nhan-dinh-chelsea-vs-arsenal-23h30-ngay-188-dung-lay-man-city-lam-thuoc-do.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-chelsea-vs-arsenal-23h30-ngay-188-dung-lay-man-city-lam-thuoc-do-172-194717.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Arsenal (23h30 ng\u00e0y 18/8): \u0110\u1eebng l\u1ea5y Man City l\u00e0m th\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111o</span><br>\r\nUn