\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Morata c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Sarri b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Morata c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/sarri-len-tieng-bao-ve-bom-xit-cua-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Morata c\u1ee7a Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\n12.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:black\">Tuy nhi\u00ean th\u00ec r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, thay \u00e1o kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1eadn v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 ghi b\u00e0n k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi so v\u1edbi n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, v\u1edbi hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a t\u1eeb th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Huddersfield.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\n12.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:black\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, Maurizio Sarri v\u1eabn b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Morata. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 kh\u00edch l\u1ec7 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Arsenal derby London:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\n12.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:black\">\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 Morata v\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. M\u1ecdi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u1ea3i qua qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng h\u00e3y c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng h\u01a1n v\u1edbi Morata, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 t\u1eebng ng\u00e0y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\n12.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:black\">N\u00f3i v\u1eady th\u00f4i ch\u1ee9 n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Morata s\u1ebd s\u1edbm kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sarri ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn \u01b0u \u00e1i, m\u1ed9t khi nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi Olivier Giroud s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t s\u00e2n c\u1ecf trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/5-cau-hoi-cho-duoc-tra-loi-trong-tran-derby-london-172-194748.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/5-cau-hoi-cho-duoc-tra-loi-trong-tran-derby-london.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/5-cau-hoi-cho-duoc-tra-loi-trong-tran-derby-london-172-194748.html\">5 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi ch\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi trong tr\u1eadn derby London k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nChelsea vs Arsenal trong k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi, c\u1ee7a nh\u1ee